=== Papers and magazine articles === * “Hadrian, the Builder of the Roman Wall” – a paper read at the monthly meeting of the Society of Antiquaries, Newcastle upon Tyne, 4. Aug. 1852 (apparently 748 pages in written form) * “The Wall of Hadrian, with Especial Reference to Recent Discoveries” (76 pages) – two lectures in 1874 * “Notice of a Stone, bearing a Rinnan Inscription, built into a Staircase in Jedburgh Abbey” in magazine 1885
